{"tid":1611361,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局：８月新申請按揭個案按月減少２６﹒５％","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:08:19.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc24c8f88a958afdeae89f6e52464b6685490760","tid":1611361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社３０日專訊》金管局公布，今年８月份新申請貸款個案按月減少２６﹒５％至１１１３３宗。新批出的按揭貸款額按月減少２﹒８％至４５３億元，當中涉及一手市場交易所批出的貸款減少３﹒６％至１０９億元；涉及二手市場交易所批出的貸款減少４﹒７％至１６０億元。至於涉及轉按交易所批出的貸款，則減少０﹒６％至１８４億元。<br />\n<br />\n  局方指，８月份新取用按揭貸款額３６６億元，按月減少１０﹒２％。以香港銀行同業拆息作為定價參考的新批按揭貸款所佔比例，由７月份的８８﹒５％上升至８月份的８９﹒１％；最優惠貸款利率作為定價的新批按揭貸款所佔比例，就由７月份的９％跌至８﹒５％。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，８月份未償還按揭貸款總額按月增加１﹒１％至１４０３２億元。按揭貸款拖欠比率維持於０﹒０２％，經重組貸款比率維持於接近０％。（ｓｋ）"},{"pid":"131d0e26f8be1273354de9c8fedad336fc237c9c","tid":1611361,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:46:44.000Z","msg":"快D 快D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2c906d92ea28ca3610740ea8c6f1dba361282c","tid":1611361,"uid":56714,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"證明多左人full pay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f895766b1a9f1f4c4ee99dde5d3b89517d50571","tid":1611361,"uid":221051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"不屑一借，個個full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bb83713adf2a55773ece036980b569d0febb6a","tid":1611361,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f49f7d1dc0549f507582986007eb92f8275064b7","tid":1611361,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"對準政權 全民公投實行雙普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}